Indriyaduka
Kusalattika
Paccayavāra
Paccayānulomapaccanīya
Indriyaduka
174.
611Indriyapaccayā nahetuyā cattāri, naārammaṇe pañca…pe…  navipāke sattarasa, naāhāre ekaṃ, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte pañca, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā pañca, novigate pañca, indriyapaccayā hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
